&lt;section class="section body-text"&gt;&lt;div class="container"&gt;
        &lt;div class="body-text"&gt;
		  &lt;p&gt;The Careers and Counselling Centre is a department in the Student Affairs Division which offers a wide range of services to students and staff in the acquisition and development of attitudes, skills, insights and understanding about themselves and their environment which are necessary for optimal growth and development.&lt;/p&gt;        		
